sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Agent
    participant C as Controller
    participant HM as Heartbeat Monitor
    participant D as Dispatcher

    Note over A,C: 1. Registration
    A->>C: RegisterMessage(name, capabilities)
    C->>C: Create/update AgentRecord (ONLINE)<br/>set last_heartbeat = now()
    C-->>A: RegisterAckMessage(agent_id)

    Note over A,C: 2. Concurrent tasks start
    par Heartbeat Loop (every 5s)
        loop Every heartbeat_interval (5s)
            A->>C: HeartbeatMessage(agent_id)
            C->>C: Update last_heartbeat = now()
        end
    and Receive Loop
        A->>A: Listen for JobAssign / Disconnect
    end

    Note over HM: 3. Monitor runs every 5s
    loop Every check_interval (5s)
        HM->>HM: Query agents where<br/>last_heartbeat < (now - 15s)<br/>AND status ≠ OFFLINE
    end

    Note over A,C: 4. Normal heartbeat flow
    A->>C: HeartbeatMessage(agent_id)
    C->>C: last_heartbeat = now()

    Note over A,HM: 5. Agent goes silent (connection lost)
    A--xC: ✗ No heartbeat for >15s

    HM->>HM: Detect stale agent<br/>(last_heartbeat expired)
    HM->>C: Close WebSocket
    HM->>HM: Agent status → OFFLINE

    alt Agent had an active job
        HM->>HM: Job status: ASSIGNED/RUNNING → QUEUED<br/>Unassign agent, clear started_at
        HM->>D: try_dispatch()
        D->>D: Find available ONLINE agent<br/>with matching capabilities
        D-->>C: Assign re-queued job<br/>to new agent
    end
